<p><a href="/scp-4937">SCP-4937 - A Deflated Balloon Dog</a> (<span style="color: green">+38</span>, <span style="color: grey">16 comments</span>)<br />
<span style="font-size:80%;"><span style="color: grey"><em><span class="odate time_1552274623 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 Mar 2019 03:23</span></em></span></span></p>
